  "title": "URGENT: Senior/Sales Engineer (semicon/mfg/equipment)",
  "description": "<p><strong>What you'll be doing</strong></p><ul><li><p>Actively prospecting and identifying new sales opportunities with potential clients</p></li><li><p>Managing the full sales lifecycle from lead generation to closing deals</p></li><li><p>Providing technical expertise and solutions for our clients' needs</p></li><li><p>Building and maintaining strong relationships with key stakeholders</p></li><li><p>Collaborating with the internal team to develop effective sales strategies</p></li><li><p>Achieving and exceeding individual and team sales targets</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>What we're looking for</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma / Degree in Engineering</p></li><li><p>Minimum 3 years of equipment sales experience</p></li><li><p>Strong technical knowledge and understanding of the products and solutions you will be selling</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication, interpersonal and negotiation skills</p></li><li><p>Proven track record of meeting and exceeding sales targets</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently and as part of a team</p></li><li><p>Willingness to travel within the region as needed</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong> or submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:ref68@trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>ref68@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg </p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: John Angeline</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1544851</p>",
